author: Hannah Miller
title: Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis issues stay-at-home order amid coronavirus outbreak
description: Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis issued a statewide order Wednesday mandating all residents to stay at home during the coronavirus outbreak.
